      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014totally spotless and still has that wonderful new car smell. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the heavy dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
