      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is an absolute benchmark of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment by a single owner. The exterior paint retains its original depth and luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, and is protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery shows no signs of bolstering wear or creasing, and the dashboard remains factory-fresh with no UV exposure. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history exclusively performed at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that looks and performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
